<D>__{that's it, son. you can go.}
<A>__{the c.o. and zim turn to other things. johnny picks up his duffel and heads out the door.}
<L>__{exterior parade ground day johnny}
<A>__{walks alone, sad. a skimmer hums by overhead and he looks after it. out across the parade ground he sees the glint of marauder power suits as recruits tumble the obstacle course.}
